Package com.opengamma.strata.product.swaption

Interface SwaptionSettlement

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CashSwaptionSettlement, PhysicalSwaptionSettlement
    public interface SwaptionSettlement
    Defines how the payoff of a swaption will be settled.

    Settlement can be physical, where an interest rate swap is created, or cash, where a monetary amount is exchanged.

    See Also:
    PhysicalSwaptionSettlement, CashSwaptionSettlement
